| sin= ආර්ය
| en= noble<br/>not ordinary<br/>precious
| bo= འཕགས་པ་
| bo-Latn=[[Wylie transliteration|Wylie]]: phags pa; <br />[[THL Simplified Phonetic Transcription|THL]]: pakpa
